FBIS4-28952 "dreas115_c_94031" FBIS-EAS-94-115 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 North Korea Delegation of Japanese Socialists on Visit Delegation of Japanese Socialists on Visit JSDP Leader Meets Hwang Chang-yop SK1406045594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0432 GMT 14 Jun 94 SK1406045594 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 14 (KCNA) -- Secretary of the Central Committee [C.C.] of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] Hwang Chang-yop Monday met and had a friendly talk at the Mansudae Assembly Hall with the delegation of the Japan Social-Democratic Party (JSDP) led by Director of the General Affairs Department of the Central Executive Committee of the Party and member of the House of Representatives Kazo Watanabe. Vice-Department Director of the C.C., the WPK Kim Yang-kon was on hand.
